    "Future research directions include extending the framework to multivariate contamination modeling, incorporating temporal dynamics for monitoring data, and developing adaptive sampling strategies guided by predictive uncertainty maps.",
    "Additionally, investigating alternative spatial ordering schemes and conditioning strategies may further improve the approximation quality under extreme censoring scenarios.",
